  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your skill on the frontlines exceeds all other shinobi. You gain a +2 to initiative rolls and your unarmed damage die becomes a 1d6. If it already a 1d6, it increases by 1 step. Starting at 11th level, whenever you deal your unarmed damage, you may add half your proficiency bonus, rounded up, to the damage roll. You may do this up to twice per turn. Starting at 18th level, your bonus to initiative becomes a +4.</p>",
